===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Lemoine [[hexagon]]''' (''plural'' '''Lemoine hexagons''')

#{{geometry}} a [[cyclic]] [[hexagon]] with [[vertex|vertices]] given by the six intersections of the edges of a triangle and the three lines that are parallel to the edges that pass through its [[symmedian point]]

